Gg_laboratory
------------------------------
I have been working on this map for awhile now and finally decided to release it.  It has some cool features in it such as a laser trap and a low gravity room.  Buyzones have been included.  Counter-terrorists start on the roof while the terrorists start in one of the rooms in the lab.

If you happen to find a bug or error let me know either through this site or on xfire (mistophlies). 

Hope you enjoy it.
